CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: BBB Foods Inc., through its subsidiaries, operates grocery retail stores in Mexico. It offers food products, drinks, hygiene and beauty products, home clean products, coffee, tea and substitutes, jellies and desserts, and baby and pet products. The company also provides branded, private label, and spot products. In addition, it offers its products through online. The company serves low-to-middle income households. The company was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Mexico City, Mexico.
